channel.description:
Hello, and welcome to Wahn Scape!
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ffyZS1C.png[/img]
WahnScape, is a new 474 ECO - PVP server. Please note that Wahn Scape is a new server, and is still looking for new development ideas, and staff. So any help is appreciated, currently there are only 5+ players on per day, and we are looking to make that about 10-15 players per day. Some Features.
All Trainable Skills - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/DUvtQal.png[/img]
New Teleport Animation - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/BrUpbly.png?1[/img]
Great Combat - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Vjifegr.png[/img]
Working Specials - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/U9QejyJ.png?1[/img]
Bosses & Monsters - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/mOocmsn.png[/img]
Recipe For Disaster Minigame - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Ea5v8x9.png[/img]
Zombie Minigame - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/4yKkPRb.png[/img]
New Level Points System & Shop - [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/TXfWiMl.png[/img]
And many more unique features! Join Today!!!!
Visit us At [url=http://wahnscape.com/]Wahnscape[/url]
Have a nice day!
EVENT: 1b+ giveaway When we reach 10 players!!!
